{"body": "The log level can be changed as per-app / env basis, and Rails logger has been by default :info for too long without much problems. I don't think it should change now, it's more a matter of preference, for some it might be good :warn, for others, :info, for others, using tags, and for some, a completely different logger. Thanks for your contribution.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/13330559", "created_at": "2013-02-09T12:18:48Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9228#issuecomment-13330559", "updated_at": "2013-02-09T12:18:48Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9228, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ebeebd3543c151009c13"}, "id": 13330559, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9228"}
